Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Like a cruel angel{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become a legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When a blue wind{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Knocks on the door to your heart{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.74,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You just gaze back at me{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}And smile oh so gently{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}So eager for something{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You touch so softly{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Those innocent eyes{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Know nothing of the fate that awaits{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.39,0:00:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But one day, you will realize{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}That upon your back{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You have wings{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}You can fly to the faraway future{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The cruel angel's thesis{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.99,0:01:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}One day, you'll take off through a window{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}If your overflowing pathos{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Leads you to betray your memories{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Then embrace the heavens and shine bright{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Become legend, young boy{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.76,0:01:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ready, Shinji?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Release final safeties!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Evangelion Unit 01, lift off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.69,0:01:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I want you to just concentrate on walking.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Take a step...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Take a step...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, pull it together!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Hurry! Hurry, you need to get up!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, stay calm!{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}It only feels like your arm is being hurt!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-Where are its defensive systems?!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-Signal inactive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Field not raised!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's not working?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-{\c}{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Left forearm damaged!{\c}{\i0}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-{\c}{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Circuits severed!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, break loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Fracture in frontal cranium!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.39,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The armor can't take much more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Skull damage! Severity unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Control neurons{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}are disconnecting in a cascade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Pilot readings lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I don't know this ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The Angels have returned.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}It's all too sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's just like 15 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Calamity never warns before striking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}This might also be considered a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It means that all our previous{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}investments were worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}That remains to be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}If it is not useful,{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}it is the same as wasted money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Information regarding the Angels{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}is spreading among the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}We need a disinformation campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Nerv's work must be carried out{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}both properly and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Those concerns are already{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}being addressed. Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}This morning at the Prime Minister's{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Office in Tokyo-2,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the government held a press--{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-{\c}{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The government claims--{\c}{\i0}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-{\c}{\i1\c&Hffffff&}UN Forces Japan were deployed--{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}They went with Scenario B-22, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Once again, the facts get buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The Public Affairs Office was ecstatic.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}They say they finally feel useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}What a bunch of optimists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.02,0:05:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I wonder.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}I think they're actually terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}They have good reason to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Well, that's certainly true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Still, Ikari... can't you manage Nerv{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}and the Evas better?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}First there was Unit 00, and now{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Unit 01 needs repairs after its debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}These bills could bankrupt a country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I hear you gave that toy to your own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.09,0:05:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}People. Time. And money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.63,0:05:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}You and your son seem to have{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}an insatiable appetite for resources.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}And this is not your only job.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The Human Instrumentality Project.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}That is your top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}That project is the only glimmer of light{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}in this desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Humanity's only hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}In any event, there can be no{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}pushing back the project's timetable
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.03,0:06:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}due to the Angels' arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Your budget request will be considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The Council will take it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Good work, Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Ikari, there's no turning back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I'm well aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Humanity's time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yeah, AC is humanity's greatest invention!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}What a triumph of science.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji's regained consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}So, what's his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}No external injuries, but they say{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}his memory's a little jumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Was there psychological contamination?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}They say there's no risk of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yeah, I'm not surprised.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}We threw him into the deep end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's no wonder.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}His cranial nerves took a lot of strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}"His heart," don't you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}NOTICE OF CONSTRUCTION{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}GUIDED MUNITIONS SYS. BUILDING NO. 25
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-Okay! Okay!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-Keep it coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.01,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Good, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Once the Evas and this city are{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}fully operational, we might have a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}You think we can win?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Ever the optimist, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Hey, a bright outlook is essential{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}for people to live their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I suppose.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Your outlook is helpful sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Paging Dr. Ugai of{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Internal Medicine Department 1.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Please contact Dr. Azuma{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}of Surgery Department 1.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Medical conference regarding Incident B{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}will take place as scheduled.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}All attendees, please gather{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}in Conference Room 2.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Are you sure they should live separately?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}For the Ikaris, life without{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}the other around is the norm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}In other words, living together{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}would be strange for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}He's living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Correct. His quarters will be{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}a room in Block Six nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-Is that acceptable?{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Are you sure, Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.93,0:09:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's fine, I prefer being alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's all the same to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I said, I'm going to have{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji live with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I got permission from the top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Don't worry,{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}I won't mess around with some kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Of course you won't!{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Don't even suggest that!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-She needs to learn to take a joke.{\c}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}-You're always doing this!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.95,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Right, then! We have to{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}celebrate in style tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.92,0:09:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Celebrate what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.13,0:09:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The arrival of a new roommate, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}You're moving, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:10:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yes. We never thought this city{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}would actually become a battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Who would?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}My husband wants me{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}and our children to evacuate, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Evacuate, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}They call this a fortress city,{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}but we can't count on it to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I get chills just thinking about{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}what happened yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.20,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}You're so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}If you don't mind,{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}we're gonna make a quick detour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Someplace special.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}kind of a desolate city, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Buildings are sprouting from the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}This is the fortress city built to counter{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}and defeat the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}This is Tokyo-3. This is our city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}And... it's the city that you protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I think your boxes of stuff{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}are already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:12:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Actually, I only moved here{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}recently, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Uh, thanks for having me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.94,0:12:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji, this is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I-I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I know it's a little cluttered,{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}but don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.21,0:12:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}She calls this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.76,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Sorry, could you put the groceries{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}in the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}snacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}and beer is all she's got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}What does she do at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Um, what's this other refrigerator for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Oh, leave that one alone. I hate to bother{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}someone when they're sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Let's eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}This is what makes life worth living!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Aren't you hungry?{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}It's TV dinner food, but it's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Well... I'm just not used to{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}eating like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Hey! We don't put up with{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}fussy eaters here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}No, I... That's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Sharing a meal with someone like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}let's do the next one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}One, two, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shoot! Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.84,0:13:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Sorry, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Okay, we've now divided up{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}all our daily chores fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Right, this place is your home{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}So no standing on ceremony for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Uh, yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}"Yes, ma'am" this and "Yes, ma'am" that!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Stop being so uptight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}You're a boy, aren't you?!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Let's hear some backbone and confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Hop into the tub{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}and wash all your cares away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.21,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The bath is life's washing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Ms. Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Oh, him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}He's a new hot-spring penguin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}His name is Pen-Pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Our other roomie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}And... maybe you could cover up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Maybe I laid on{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}the cheerfulness too thick.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.71,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}He might see right through it.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Ms. Misato Katsuragi...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I guess she's not a bad person.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The bath is life's washing machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But... I tend to remember{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}all the bad things when I'm in the bath.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Father...{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}and Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}How was Rei, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.28,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I understand you visited her{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}at the hospital this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.50,0:15:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}She'll be back on her feet{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}in 20 days or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}We need to get Unit 00 up and running{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}and ready for reactivation by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}This will be rough... on those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}No one else can pilot the Evas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}As long as they're alive,{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}that's what they'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Regardless of how they feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}SHINJI'S ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}SCHOOL TRANSFER FORM:{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}SHINJI IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.91,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}True, he was put through the wringer.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I don't know if he'll do it again.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Making sure he's operational{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}is part of your job.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I'm afraid.{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Not sure how I should approach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Whining already?{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}You were so dramatic about taking him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Shove it!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}When I said that,{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I just saw Shinji as a means to an end.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.89,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}I'm no different from Ritsuko.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}He beat that Angel.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.19,0:17:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}So why aren't I happy about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Another ceiling I've never seen before.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}No surprise...{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Nothing about this city is familiar.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.58,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}This is your home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Why am I even here?{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Skull damage, severity unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Operational integrity compromised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Synchrograph inverting!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Neural pulse flow is reversing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shut down circuits! Block the flow, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I can't! Shutdown signal rejected!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}It's not getting through!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji's status?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Zero biometrics! Condition unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Unit 01 completely shut down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.33,0:18:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I guess that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Abort operation!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}Pilot rescue has top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Emergency plug eject, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I can't! System is{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}completely unresponsive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.30,0:18:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}The Eva has reactivated!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.19,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Impossible! It should be{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}completely non-operational!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-Has it gone...{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-...berserk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}We've won.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}An A.T. Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's no use!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}As long as that field is up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}...it can't touch the Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.69,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-Left arm restored!{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}-Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Unit 01 has also raised an A.T. Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}The Angel's phase space{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}is being neutralized!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}No, it's {\c}{\i1\c&Hffffff&}corroding{\c}{\i0\c&Hffffff&} it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It tore through that A.T. Field{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}like it was nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}It's self-destructing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}What happened to the Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}That's the Evas'...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}...true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Circuits connected.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.20,0:20:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}System back online.{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Graph readings at normal levels.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Pilot's vitals confirmed.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.54,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Expedite unit recovery.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.42,0:20:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Pilot rescue has top priority!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Shinji? I'm coming in for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}I forgot to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}People will thank you{\c}\N{\c&Hffffff&}for what you did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}You should be proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.19,0:21:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Good night, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}Keep it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:22:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}With Shinji drifting through his new life,{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.06,0:23:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}there was little hope{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}of him ever making friends.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.23,0:23:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}But the fact that he's the Eva's pilot{\c}{\i0}\N{\i1\c&Hffffff&}makes him a celebrity.{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.19,0:23:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}Next episode! "The Silent Phone"!{\c}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&Hffffff&}More fan service coming up next time, too!{\c}{\i0}
